layout.house_prompt: A pet clinic with a reception, a waiting room, two exam rooms, a surgery room, a corridor, and a bathroom. The reception has a reception desk with a computer. The waiting room has four chairs and a water dispenser. The first exam room has an exam table and a cabinet. The second exam room has an exam table and a scale. The surgery room has a surgery table and a surgical light. The corridor has a bench. The bathroom has a toilet and a sink.

reception.text_description: A clean modern veterinary clinic reception area with a reception desk and a computer; scrub-able washable wall finish; seamless slip-resistant commercial resilient flooring; primary public arrival point.

waiting_room.text_description: A clean modern veterinary clinic waiting room with four chairs and a water dispenser; scrub-able washable wall finish; seamless slip-resistant commercial resilient flooring; strong natural light via exterior windows; connects to reception and corridor.

corridor.text_description: A clean modern veterinary clinic public clinical corridor with a bench; scrub-able washable wall finish; seamless slip-resistant commercial resilient flooring; includes a controlled staff-only door to the back-of-house zone leading to surgery; has a secondary staff/service exterior egress door at the clinical end.

exam_room_1.text_description: A clean modern veterinary exam room with an exam table and a cabinet; scrub-able washable wall finish; seamless slip-resistant commercial resilient flooring; bright clinical lighting.

exam_room_2.text_description: A clean modern veterinary exam room with an exam table and a scale; scrub-able washable wall finish; seamless slip-resistant commercial resilient flooring; bright clinical lighting.

bathroom.text_description: A clean modern clinic bathroom with a toilet and a sink; ceramic tile floor and tiled walls for easy cleaning and privacy; single-door access for privacy/safety.

staff_hall.text_description: A clean modern staff-only pass-through behind reception; scrub-able washable wall finish; seamless slip-resistant commercial resilient flooring; connects reception to the clinical corridor and surgery.

surgery_room.text_description: A clean modern veterinary surgery room with a surgery table and a surgical light; scrub-able washable wall finish; seamless slip-resistant commercial resilient/epoxy-style flooring for sterile cleaning; staff-only access.
